    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I'm hesitant to rush to make a call, actually. So far there's at least a little bit of risk of permanent harm with each of the options considered, and the cost of doing nothing isn't too high. The `return my_message_module_pb2.MyMessage()` in\r\n\r\n```python\r\nmy_servicer_context.set_code(my_desired_code)\r\nreturn my_message_module_pb2.MyMessage()\r\n```\r\n\r\nis cosmetically unattractive, but that's it. Is there some reason to rush ahead on this?"
  },
