    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "This is a Python specific API design decision and allowing custom status codes (via this API or set_code) is an orthogonal and cross-language design decision that we did not open up here, but the short answer is no, as discussed on https://github.com/grpc/grpc/issues/13321."
